  "description": "<p><strong>《分裂细胞：黑名单》(Splinter Cell：Blacklist)正在给开发商育碧(Ubisoft)一个测试新的拍摄和剪辑方法。新方法混合了真人演员、先进的动作捕捉和一个新的虚拟摄像机系统。</strong>育碧在多伦多向Outside Xbox展示了这个虚拟摄像机，混合了增强现实(AR)和实时视频编辑，允许一名摄像机操作人员在以前拍摄的场景中自由导航，而且视角会随着他们的走动而改变。<br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2dcae160/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242504.htm&amp;t=%E8%82%B2%E7%A2%A7%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A8%E3%80%8A%E5%88%BA%E5%AE%A2%E4%BF%A1%E6%9D%A1V%E3%80%8B%E7%AD%89%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E4%B8%AD%E8%BF%90%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%BA%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%9E%E6%B7%B7%E6%8B%8D%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242504.htm&amp;t=%E8%82%B2%E7%A2%A7%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A8%E3%80%8A%E5%88%BA%E5%AE%A2%E4%BF%A1%E6%9D%A1V%E3%80%8B%E7%AD%89%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E4%B8%AD%E8%BF%90%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%BA%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%9E%E6%B7%B7%E6%8B%8D%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242504.htm&amp;t=%E8%82%B2%E7%A2%A7%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A8%E3%80%8A%E5%88%BA%E5%AE%A2%E4%BF%A1%E6%9D%A1V%E3%80%8B%E7%AD%89%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E4%B8%AD%E8%BF%90%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%A2%9E%E5%BC%BA%E7%8E%B0%E5%AE%9E%E6%B7%B7%E6%8B%8D%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242504.htm&amp;t=%E8%82%B2%E7%A2%A7%E5%B0%86%E5%9C%A8%E3%80%8A%E5%88%BA%E5%AE%A2%E4%BF%A1%E6%9D%A1V%E3%80%8B%E7%A